sub_title: Asset management, onderhoud en risico beheersing
summary:
In my career I have chosen to complete my Bachelor degree in the evening hours. As a result of this strategy I was able to gain practical work experiences at a young age.

I have experiences in leading projects from A to Z. I love to come up with innovative out-of-the-box ideas that make the work more efficient. 

I am a leader with strong influence skills with the aim of meeting the business objectives. Enthusiastically engaging, collaboration and involving people in a team, project or change with a practical & pragmatic approach are elements that describe me as a person.
